Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

#KinniSoni #DarshanRaval #ShrutiSharma #naushadkhan #OutOfControl #Newsong2024 #IndieMusicLabel  

Here‚Äôs the second track from Darshan Raval‚Äôs album 'Out of Control' ‚Äì 'Kinni Soni', featuring Shruti Sharma. With Darshan‚Äôs powerful vocals and Gurpreet Saini‚Äôs sharp lyrics, this song dives headfirst into the wild and crazy side of love. It‚Äôs all about the uncontrollable emotions, passion, and that electric energy you feel when you're swept up in love. If you‚Äôre ready for a ride filled with pure madness, this one‚Äôs for you. Get ready to feel it all!

snippet.title: Taaza Khabar | Season 2 | Official Trailer | Hotstar Specials | Sept 27 | BB Ki Vines Productions
snippet.description:
Don't forget to watch the series "Taaza Khabar" starring Bhuvan Bam, streaming exclusively on Disney+ Hotstar! http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Karza aur gunah chukaane padhte hain! Kabhi kabhi marr ke bhi..

Vardaan ya shraap? Kismat ya mehnat? Jeevan ya maut?
Vasya ki kahani ka naya adhyay dekhiye Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 mein, streaming from September 27, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar's hit fantasy-drama series returns with Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar Season 2, diving deeper into the consequences of Vasya's miraculous gift. Set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai, this season promises to take viewers on an intense journey as Vasya grapples with the loss of his power and faces life-threatening challenges.

Directed by Himank Gaur and produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under BB Ki Vines Productions, the show continues to be penned by the talented writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal. Bhuvan Bam reprises his role as Vasant Gawde, joined by Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Jaaved Jaaferi, Deven Bhojani, Shilpa Shukla, Prathmesh Parab, and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.

This season explores the thin line between blessing and curse as Vasya navigates a world where his actions have far-reaching consequences. With higher stakes and deeper emotional complexity, Taaza Khabar Season 2 promises to deliver a gripping tale of redemption, morality, and the human spirit's resilience in the face of adversity.

#TaazaKhabarSeason2 #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

ABOUT:

Preparation time - 60 mins
No of modak - 25 (approx)

Ingredients:
Rice flour - 1 cups
Water -1.75 cups

For Stuffing :
Fresh coconut - 2 cups
Jaggery - 1 cup
Cardamom powder -1/2 tsp
Ghee -1 tsp

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her father‚Äôs illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her father‚Äôs illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen

snippet.title: #VenkyAnil3 x #SVC58 Vinayaka Chavithi Special Video | Venkatesh | Anil Ravipudi | Dilraju
snippet.description:
Watch #VenkyAnil3 x #SVC58 Vinayaka Chavithi Special Video!!

The extensive schedule of Victory Venkatesh, blockbuster machine Anil Ravipudi‚Äôs new film #VenkyAnil03 made under the esteemed production house Sri Venkateswara Creations was wrapped up. In this 30+ days long schedule, the makers filmed crucial sequences involving the lead cast, songs, and also action part.

On the occasion, and also to wish everyone on Vinayaka Chaturthi, offering a glimpse into the cheerful atmosphere on set. The video captures the joy and camaraderie among the cast, with smiles all around, perfectly embodying Charlie Chaplin‚Äôs sentiment that, ‚Äúa day without laughter is a day wasted.

#VenkyAnil3 is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #VenkateshDaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash. Regular Shoot begins soon and will be released grandly for SANKRANTHI 2025. 

Cast: Venkatesh Daggubati, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Aishwarya Rajesh, Upendra Limaye, Rajendra Prasad, Sai Kumar, Naresh, VT Ganesh, Muralidhar Goud, Pammi Sai, Sai Srinivas, Anand Raj, Chaitanya Jonnalagadda, Mahesh Balaraj, Pradeep Kabra, and Chitti etc.,

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Teaser
snippet.description:
Be There and Be Square. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie,‚Äù directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.

The film also stars Emma Myers (‚ÄúWednesday‚Äù), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (‚ÄúThe Color Purple‚Äù), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (‚ÄúJust Mercy, ‚ÄúLisey‚Äôs Story‚Äù), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn‚Äôt just help you craft, it‚Äôs essential to one‚Äôs survival!  Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses,‚Äù ‚ÄúNacho Libre‚Äù) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The director‚Äôs creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (‚Äú127 Hours,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), editor James Thomas (‚ÄúPok√©mon: Detective Pikachu‚Äù, the ‚ÄúBorat‚Äù films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), and costume designer Amanda Neale (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok,‚Äù the ‚ÄúLEGO¬Æ‚Äù movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Moj√§ng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie.‚Äù  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.description:
Goat (Tamil Movie) - American Theater Experience & Review

Watching "Goat" in the U.S. was electrifying! The theater buzzed with excitement from a diverse audience and the energy was contagious as everyone cheered and reacted together, making it a fun and communal experience.

Review: "Goat" showcases Thalapathy Vijay in a phenomenal dual role, delivering a powerful and versatile performance that‚Äôs the heart of the film. He seamlessly switches between contrasting characters, adding depth and charisma that keeps viewers hooked. Yuvan Shankar Raja‚Äôs background score is a perfect blend, elevating every scene with pulsating beats that amplify the film's intensity and emotional core.

The screenplay is tight and engaging, with unexpected twists that keep the audience on their toes. Venkat Prabhu‚Äôs direction is spot-on, expertly balancing action, drama, and humor, making "Goat" a standout experience. While the pacing dips slightly in places, the combination of stellar performances, gripping storytelling, and an unforgettable BGM make "Goat" a must-watch!

snippet.description:
Sneak Peek 1 for the Clash of Clans Update bring Clan Notice Boards, Loot Changes and many QoL Improvements. Judo Sloth Gaming explains all of the information released today. Most notably the Loot Changes will increase the amount of resources you can farm. This is because the amount of loot you can lose from storages on defense is being adjusted. In today‚Äôs Josh Talks Hindi video, we meet an incredible source of inspiration, Kumar Gaurav Sir. His journey has been full of challenges, but he never gave up and turned his dreams into reality.

Born into a humble family with limited financial resources, Kumar Gaurav Sir faced numerous obstacles throughout his education. Despite these hardships, he worked hard to pursue his dreams. To support himself financially, he started giving tuition classes and gradually moved forward.

After completing his education, Kumar Gaurav Sir joined Utkarsh as a content writer. Through his dedication and hard work, he quickly earned recognition and became one of the top teachers at Utkarsh. His writing skills and unique teaching methods became a source of inspiration for students.

Kumar Gaurav Sir's story teaches us that no matter how difficult life gets, with determination and persistence, any goal can be achieved. His journey encourages us to stay positive and keep moving forward, no matter the obstacles.

Don't miss this video and get inspired by Kumar Gaurav Sir's motivational story to work hard and make your dreams come true.

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Mr. McMahon | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Mr. McMahon chronicles the rise and fall of Vince McMahon, controversial businessman and co-founder of WWE. From his transformation of the WWE from a small, regional business into a global entertainment powerhouse to the explosive sexual misconduct allegations that led to his eventual resignation, this six-episode series offers a deep dive into McMahon‚Äôs life and his enduring franchise. Culled from over 200 hours of interviews with McMahon himself (prior to his resignation), his family members, business associates and some of the most iconic names in wrestling history, as well as the journalists who uncovered McMahon‚Äôs allegations ‚Äî filmmaker Chris Smith (Tiger King) and executive producer Bill Simmons (30 for 30) present an unflinching, no-holds-barred look at one of the most enigmatic figures in sports entertainment.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81179220

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Mr. McMahon | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

WWE experienced record-breaking highs and crushing lows under Vince McMahon's leadership. This docuseries delves into the mogul's controversial reign.
